Other people like the saying because it means that Portland is still a place where it is good to be different.

Portland is getting more people with money from California. There are many new buildings for these people. But Portland is still different. Being weird does not mean that everyone is nice to each other. But it means that people accept things that are different. Portland has modern things and problems like the rest of the country. People buy things from China.

There are many ways to be different. Portland has many different kinds of people. There are people who do yoga, people who dress in a special way, and people who work in business. Maybe being weird means that people do not take things too seriously.

In my neighborhood, there are colorful houses. People have gardens with plants and flowers. There are boxes on the street with things people do not want. These boxes can have clothes or books or other things. Sometimes, people find something special in these boxes.

Walking through my neighborhood is amazing. This is what Portland is all about to me. But there are many different kinds of people in Portland. Some people would never take clothes from a box on the street. These people go to yoga with goats or watch soccer games. Portland has people who like many things. Portland has people who follow their dreams or dream about following their dreams. They spend time at bars.

Portland has a problem with drugs. Drug problems are often mental health problems. The rain and clouds may make people feel sad. Portland also has many people who do not have homes. People come to Portland because there are services to help them. But the services are not enough. People who have homes have mixed feelings about people who do not have homes. This is not weird.

The mountains are always there. They are in the north. They see the sun come up and go down. I forget about them sometimes. I am busy with work and life. But they are still there. They do not change. They do not care about problems. When I am sad, I look at the mountains. They help me feel better.

I moved here for college. The mountains near my school were very nice. The school is pretty, with buildings, ponds, and trees. But the mountains are the best. The town is also nice. There are many good places to get coffee. I can walk or take a bus to the center of town. The old buildings are interesting. The town feels busy. But it is still quiet.

Near the library, the town is small and peaceful. The town is different in different places. It is fun to explore. I have made good memories here. I have walked with friends in the park and seen movies at the theater. 

Sometimes, I have sad memories here, too. The ponds are good for thinking. I have cried by the pond when I feel sad. I see turtles, ducks, and bugs. They live their lives. I think about my own life. I walk past the pond, the park, and the houses. I walk until I see the sun rise. The sun shines on the palm trees. I am walking north.

The mountains are there. They are big and strong. They are higher than any building. They make me feel strong.

If you go to Bensonhurst, Brooklyn, it is easy to find. Public transport is good. It is popular in New York City. Bensonhurst is a city area. You will feel like you are in New York City. See many Asian stores.

Twenty years ago, many Asian people moved to Bensonhurst. You see an Asian store on each block. Supermarkets and laundromats are popular. They are good for people who live here. The food is good and cheap. It is very easy to shop.

Near my home, there are four Asian supermarkets. They are close together. It is easy to buy food. 

Bensonhurst is not only Asian. There are people from many places.  There are new Americans and their children. Many stores are Asian owned. 

There is a new park near here. There are many basketball courts. There is a big field for soccer or baseball. There are handball courts, swings, and a water fountain. The park is for everyone.

There are not many big buildings in Bensonhurst. There are homes for many people to share. Most homes are two-family houses.

The people are kind. But, they are very loud. Cars play loud music. People drive fast. It can be loud in the morning.

At night, be careful. Bensonhurst is safe, but people can be mean. You may see people who want to fight. You may see thieves.

A few years ago, I was hurt by a bully. Recently, someone took a package. People steal packages here. 

In New York City, people must clean up after their dogs. But, people do not do this in Bensonhurst.  You will see dog waste. Be careful!

Where I live, there are not many sidewalks. The ground goes down, down, down. My house is at the top of the biggest hill. People call it the "work out hill". Many runners go up the hill. The street has no sidewalks. People walk on the road. The road is bad in some places. It is hard to drive. 

The wires for phones and electricity are old. They look bad. It rains a lot. Branches fall on the wires. The workers fix them often. The wires look patched.

There are many tall trees. People do not like the trees. They cut down many trees. The trees block the view of the ocean. Houses are built high on the hill. They have big windows. People want to see the ocean.

The sunset is pretty. The water shines. The sky is orange.

It rains a lot. The sun is often hidden. The days are gray. Moss grows on everything. It grows on houses, cars, and fences. My car was green with moss. I had to clean it.

There are not many children here. There is a school nearby. Most people are old. Many are retired. People have dogs. The dogs run around. They go into houses if the door is open. I found a dog in my house once.

Rabbits are common. Some are big. Gardeners do not like them. They dig up plants. My cats like rabbits. They have chased many rabbits away. There are birds here. Small birds, big birds, and hawks.

There are no stores nearby. There are a few restaurants by the water. They sell seafood. There is no big beach. The rocks by the water are fun to throw.

The bay is not very wide. You can see the other side.

I live in a suburb. It is in a small town. The town is in the south of the United States. My street is between two big roads. There is much traffic. But the area is quiet. Not many people move here. I know most people. They do yard work and other things each day. In the winter, we go sledding down a hill. We live at the front of our street. We see everyone. We know the cars that people drive. We see new cars. We take note of them. Some neighbors walk. Some walk their dogs. Kids ride bikes. This is normal. We are home a lot. We work from home. There are four of us. My wife, me, and our two daughters. They are eleven and fourteen. People know us. We go outside. We play, even in the rain. We have a grill. We cook outside. It smells good. Many people cut grass. We hear lawn mowers often. The grass grows from March to October. We have many trees. It was a wood area. There is much shade. But there are many leaves in the fall. We rake and burn the leaves. I like the smell. It means fall is here. We have not had much winter. It feels like a long fall. Our garage is in back. We use the front door rarely. I work in the garage. I fix my truck. When the garage door is open, I feel close to my neighbors. Holidays are quiet. Thanksgiving is busy. Neighbors visit. There are many cars. It is like this for Mother's Day and Christmas. I like living here. If it was not a through street, it would be perfect.

My area is in the center of the high desert. There is dirt everywhere. If you do not live here, you may not know how it feels to see only brown. When you see a green lawn, you know someone works hard to keep it. When I first lived here in the 1990s, houses were far apart. Now, there are many new houses. This place looks more like a city now. But most places are changing. People here are kind. Like any city, there are good parts and bad parts. My neighborhood has many friendly old people. The stores are big chains, like Food 4 Less and Smart & Final. If you want foods like Whole Foods, you must travel. I see many construction jobs here. I think this is because the city is still growing. There is a lot of space to build. This scares me. I like it the way it is. I left a big city and do not want to go back. I work in construction. I install drywall and T-bars. I like the animals in my home. People come to the high desert for many reasons. One reason is the beauty of the desert. The desert is dry and hot. It has many plants and animals. People who live here must learn about the animals so they can live together. My family and I like the animals. My children love lizards and bugs. They are outside now, trying to find them. We have some things to see here. Victorville is a good place for families. It is different. If you visit, go to the San Bernardino County Fair. It has many activities and fun things to do. Visit Wrightwood to see snowy mountains. Take lessons in winter sports. If you like history, go to the Victor Valley Museum. It has rocks, bones, old things, and things that show how the city grew.

My neighborhood is different. I live on a college campus. My friends in the dormitory are my community. The campus is also my neighborhood, but not as much as the dormitory. My neighborhood has things like houses, people, stores, and parks, like other neighborhoods. 

Let's talk about the "houses." There are three types: apartments, regular houses, and dormitory houses. Apartments have 2-4 people per room, with 4-6 rooms per floor. Each building has about 20 people.

Regular houses are for rent by school staff. They have 2-4 bedrooms. Only a few of these houses are in the neighborhood. Dorm rooms are the most common. They have two people per room. 

My school has many different people. Students from all over live here. Older students live in apartments. Newer students live in dorms.  

The school has many stores. There are places to eat, and stores that sell clothes and food. There is also a park where everyone can play. The park is clean and safe because everyone takes care of it.

I live in this area for ten years. When I first came, I was sad. I moved from Riverdale to Stockbridge. I miss my old home. My parents wanted a good place for me and my sister. Our new home is good. I made friends and some enemies at school.

I know some neighbors well. Mr. Glen and his children live next door. Dennis also lives close by. They are good people. I like them. I went to Mr. Glen's wedding. It was fun. I hope to have a wedding like that someday.

Mr. Glen's wife threw a small strap. I caught it. I did not catch the flowers. We danced all night. I met one of Mr. Glen's daughters. Her name is Marsharii.

Our neighborhood is like a maze. I use a GPS to find my way. I have been to some parts of the neighborhood with my friends, Kason and Curtis. We play video games and have fun.

I like to go to the park. It is peaceful. I feel calm there. I bring sticks and practice my balance. I bring a wooden sword sometimes. I like to practice. There are basketball and tennis courts. I do not play often, but they are there.

My dad taught me tennis when I was young. I had fun.

I have had many fun times in this neighborhood. The best is yet to come.

My home is near the college I go to. I like living there. There are many apartment buildings. There are a few good restaurants and bars. They are not very expensive. One bar is new. It is more expensive, but the drinks are good. Most people are nice. They are college students or have low wages. The apartments are not expensive. There are many children because there is a school close by. I do not know my neighbors. I do not want to. They smoke a lot of marijuana. The building manager put an air freshener near their door. My boyfriend and I think it is funny. 

The buildings are old. Some have new insides. There are new apartments down the street. I do not like them. They are not built well. The rent is high. The managers can charge a lot because they are near the college. There is a cheap restaurant near me. They use paper plates. Most food is heated in a microwave. Across from it is a gas station. I hear it is not a good place to work.

The city fixed the road last summer. There is a wide sidewalk now. There is grass on the sides of the road. The area is nicer. My building is near many trees. They cut down some trees, but there are many left. Behind my building is a line of trees. Then there are more apartments. I live on 42nd street. Behind me is 43rd street. It is not as nice. The sidewalks are bad. The buildings look old. There are many trees there too. They may hide the buildings.

There has been some crime on 43rd street. But I cannot blame just one place. There are apartments across from me with a lot of crime. I like where I live. I can afford it. There are many things near me. I like that the university is close. There are two bus stops. I can go to the store and downtown easily.

My area has small homes on a road with no exit. The homes are close, but not too close. They look like single homes. Each home is yellow with white porches and green roofs. Most people know each other. We talk in the evenings. Small children play games and fly kites. It is nice to have a calm place.  This is different from the busy city. It is like going back in time. We have fields and trees. The sky is blue with white clouds. But there is a problem. We had a warning about a tornado. Last night, we heard the alarm. We went to a safe place. I took my small dog to the bathtub with my purse and pillows. My big dog stayed in the living room and barked. The storm had big hail. It made a loud sound. The road was hot. The hail melted quickly. After the storm, the sun came out and it rained. A rainbow appeared. I took a picture with my camera. My friends and family liked the picture. The street was quiet for a while. Then people came home. It was back to normal. People talked and children played. I like this area. I moved here from another state. I like the way people talk. I live in a small home with two bedrooms and two bathrooms. All the homes look the same outside.  The insides are different. Some are small. I like to walk to a big field. There is a pond there. I see deer. I hear a frog sing in the morning. This is a good place to live. It is near a city. We hear roosters crow in the morning. It is like a small village. There is a donkey on a farm nearby. It makes a loud sound at night. I am happy to live here.

I move to this area when I was about to start eighth grade. It was hard to make friends at first. But I make friends with two boys. One lives two houses from me. The other boy lives on my street. They do not live here now. But I still remember them. Most of the same people live here now. My area is like other areas in America. It has two-story houses. I hear kids play outside every weekend. The area is quiet most days. I never have a problem with people here. People leave each other alone. I order things online. I never have a problem with my packages. I trust my neighbors. There is a park near my house. I have good memories there. I play basketball, football, and baseball there with other boys. I also get hurt there once. I get hit in the nose. But the good memories are better. Now I go to the park with my cousin's children. They are young. They like to play on swings and slides. They like to go to the park. The park makes me feel happy. My area has many different kinds of people. There are many kinds of food nearby. You can find Chinese, Indian, Mexican, and Italian food. People use apps to get food. They use apps like GrubHub and DoorDash. Fast food is very popular. There are many pizza places too. The stores here have everything you need. There are dry cleaners, a Walgreens, a CVS, and a Jewel-Osco.  There is even an Indian store. I like my area. I see bad things on the news. People have bad neighbors. I am happy with my neighbors.

My town is small. It is in South Carolina. It is not like other towns. But it is important for farming. Johnston is known as the Peach Capital of the World. The town is mostly farms. There are many peach trees and cows.

The houses are far apart. Most are two stories. Some have metal roofs. Some have gray shingles. The houses are not near the road. They are behind the road. There is one stop light in town.

There are three places for fast food. One is Hong Kong, a small Chinese restaurant. Another is Fiesta, a Mexican restaurant. The third is Gary's, a burger place. There used to be a pizza place, but it closed. There is a small pharmacy called Maxwell and Halford Drug. They are known for Cherry Coca-Cola.

There is one grocery store called IGA. It is expensive. People go to a Walmart in another town for most of their food. The most popular store is Dollar General. It sells many things.

There is a small furniture store called Possibilities Furniture & More. They have movers who deliver furniture. There is a pet store next to the furniture store.

The doctor's office and the veterinarian are away from the main part of town.

There is one elementary school. Students go to middle and high school in another town.

There are no parks. But they are building a park.

There are not many things to do in town. There are no movies, bowling, or places for kids to play. But it is a nice town. It is small. You can drive through it quickly.

I first heard of my place on a radio show. The show was about people who had gone missing. This was a surprise. All the apartments in my area cost more than one thousand dollars each month. I had not heard this story. My friends had not heard it either. Maybe it is hard to live here. I know some of my friends cry at night. Things are expensive here, but we have learned to spend less money. You like old toys from the market. You like old clothes. You smell less when you are an adult. You might smoke. You might just get used to things. But the market is always there. The smell of being an adult is old magazines on a piano. It stays on the leather even after you wash it.

There are three stores to buy old things near me. If you walk far, you can go to two stores that give to charity. You can also go to a library, a store with old books, and a store with strange things.

Downtown is busy. Cars and people are everywhere in the morning. But the stores are quiet. No matter how many people or cars pass, the stores are still quiet. It is a good place to spend an afternoon. Every year, there are more cars and people. It is a growing city. It has a big company that sells things online. It is still changing. It reminds me of New York City. Everyone is working on their own goals. No one asks for much. You can be alone and quiet. People will leave you alone. It is not like the South, where people care a lot. People do not ask questions here. You can hide if you want. The city keeps moving like waves on the beach. It is a good place to live.

My neighbors are musicians. There is a pianist next door. There are singers upstairs. There is always something happening. We are not strangers. We are friends. We help each other. I am lucky to live here. I like my neighbors. They are kind to me. I keep my place clean and I share food with them. They do the same for me. I bring them mail and they bring me mail. I like seeing them and I think they like seeing me. I live in a big, modern building, but my neighbors make me feel like I am not alone.

My area is a suburb. It is like many other suburbs. There is a homeowner's association. When you enter, you see many houses. The houses are all alike. There are yards with grass, rocks, and short driveways. There are also small trees. Every house has a garage for two cars. The roads are new and in good shape. There are no holes. Most houses are one story. Some are two stories.

The mailboxes are not like other suburbs. There are no mailboxes in front of each house. There is a big box for the mail at the end of the street. People use a key to get to their mail. There are also two big boxes for packages.

My house is on the edge of the city. My area is part city and part country. There is a lot of land. There are pools for the people who live here. They are safe and locked. There are also walking paths. People can walk their dogs or take a walk.

Many people in my area are retired. It is a safe place. People look out for each other. There are also some middle-aged and young people here.

The city is big, but it feels small. It has many stores. There is one mall. It is not very big. It takes me fifteen minutes to drive to the mall. There are many stores there. There are stores with good food and stores with cheap food.

My area is safe and nice. We have pools and walking paths. It is not close to stores, but we can drive to them.

I live in a small town. It is near a big city. My home is on the east side of the town. It is poor area.  Homes are old. Many people are poor. My neighbors are nice. They say hello when I walk by. Crime is not bad. There are a few bad things that happen, but not many. My neighbors lost their son in a shooting last year. It was sad. We are safe at home. 

The town has a big problem with drugs. Many people use drugs. Many people die from drugs. There are places to help people stop using drugs.

My son goes to a good school. The teachers are nice. He does not have to worry about bad kids. The school has food for all children. 

The town has been fixing things. They have fixed roads and parks. Most of the good things are on the other side of town. My side is old.

We like living here. The people are nice. The school is good. We have stores to buy things. Our house is not big, but it is good. We have lived here for a long time. We like it here.

My area has much culture. It is on a hill, with buildings with history. I live in a tall building across from an old theater. Close by is a bar that many people like to visit on warm nights. Often, people wait in line to go in. Close by is a big park. It is small for the city. Around the park is concrete with many steps. In winter, people without homes make rows of tents. It rains a lot, and it is hard to stay warm. They stay close to the park and to a place where they can bathe. 

I like my city. It has old buildings and nice places. I like the people here. Hilltop was a bad place with gangs. People talk about the police trying to make it better. The people work hard to keep it clean. They care about their city. Some people say that white people should not walk alone at night. I think this is old thinking. Maybe they see me as one of them.

Hilltop reminds me that people are different. People make judgments based on skin color. That is not fair. I know one thing: Hilltop is my home. I feel safe there, even at night. People are kind to me.

I live in Rural America. I live in a small town in Michigan. The town is near farms and small cities. There are no big city stores. There is no Wal-Mart, Target, or Applebee’s. You must drive to go to these places. I live near water. Lake Michigan is on one side of my town. Lake Charlevoix is on the other side. 

My neighborhood is small. The houses are not close together. The houses are old. Some are new. Many houses have basements. You can see the basements from the street. Many houses have aluminum siding. The houses are many colors. Most houses have yards. Some yards have trampolines and playsets. Some have gardens and fences for animals. 

The people here work hard. They raise families. You see children playing outside. You see people walking dogs and biking. Neighbors know each other. You can tell who lives here and who does not. People greet each other. 

The yards are kept clean. The grass is cut. Plants and bushes are trimmed. This is not a fancy neighborhood. It is a good place to raise a family. It is quiet and safe. 

Near my home is the police station and jail. The health department is next door. The recycling center is down the road. People use these services. We have baseball and softball fields. You can hear the announcers. Our small airport is nearby. You can hear planes taking off and landing. You can walk to get ice cream. You can walk to the center of town. My children can ride their bikes to the park. It is a great place to live.
